<h4 style="margin:18px 0 8px;color:var(--bc-text-secondary,#555);">User Profiles &amp; Settings <span style="background:#fd7e14;color:#fff;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:12px;">HIGH</span></h4>
